title: Jack_Johnson_Kokua_Festival_2008.mov
description:
Live concert of Jack Johnson at the 5th annual Kokua festival Honolulu Hawaii April 2008
Filmed over two nights april 19th and 20th 2008. Original encoded for on MSN in concert.
Now encoded as a Quicktime movie with chaptertrack, so you can easily switch to another song.
